<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Feedback Response</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.13.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .email-header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #FF8012;
            /* Updated golden color */
            padding: 30px 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .email-header img {
            max-width: 180px;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 40px;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .email-body p {
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .email-body a {
            color: #FF8012;
            /* Updated golden color for links */
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #FF8012;
            /* Updated golden color for button */
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #FF8012;
            /* Updated golden color for footer links */
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .response-section {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            border-left: 4px solid #FF8012;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .response-section p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .response-section strong {
            color: #FF8012;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <table class="email-container" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
            <td class="email-header">
                <img src="../public/assets/icons/reachmate.png" alt="Logo">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="email-body">
                <p>Hello <strong>
                        <%= full_name %>
                    </strong>,</p>

                <p>Thank you for reaching out to us! We appreciate your feedback and wanted to take a moment to address
                    your inquiry.</p>

                <p>We understand your concern regarding <%= query_topic %>, and we are currently working to resolve it.
                        Your thoughts are valuable to us, and we will keep you updated on the progress. If you need any
                        further assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to us again.</p>

                <p>For more information or to explore other related topics, feel free to visit our <a
                        href="<%= help_link %>">Help Center</a>.</p>

                <!-- Response to the user's query -->
                <div class="response-section">
                    <p><strong>Your Query:</strong>
                        <%= user_query %>
                    </p>
                    <p><strong>Our Response:</strong>
                        <%= response_text %>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <a href="<%= response_link %>" style="color:white;" class="cta-button">Get More Help</a>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="footer">
                <p>If you have any more questions, please visit our <a href="<%= help_link %>">Help Center</a>.</p>
                <p>Follow us on <a href="<%= social_link %>">social media</a> for updates.</p>
                <p>&copy; ReachMate 2025. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p><a href="<%= privacy_link %>">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="<%= terms_link %>">Terms of Service</a>
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>